title: There once was..
author: MONKEY_LION
pages:
#- There once was a man named pucker,
Some said he was a fucker,

People chased him and hunted him but he was to quick,
So they dismissed of this idea with a flick,


#- This continued for years and years,
On untamedears,

Eventually the caught him,
But they understimated the coding,
#- Pucker was free due to a glitch in the system,
Fortunatley they cant pearl him, he's to quick for them.

THE END 

